    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Benedictus">Benedicti</name></persName>
                        viene posto da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops"
                            >Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis
                            <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine (…), in
                        casa et res illa in loco ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/239"
                            >Titulo</placeName>, pertenentes ecclesie vestre <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/284" key="#Baptismal_churches">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, quod est <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebem
                            battismalis</rs>, sita in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/239"
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">Quaratiana</placeName>, qui est de
                        suppotestatem ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> nostro
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas <persName><name ref="Ansfrit"
                            >Ansifridi</name></persName> ad manus suas abuit; casa vero ipsa cum
                        fundamento et edeficio suo, seo curte, orto, terris, vineis, olivis, silvis,
                        virgareis, pratis, pascuis, cultis rebus vel incultis, omnia (…) in integrum
                        (…). Obbligo: in ipsa casa residere et abitare debeamus et tam ipsa casa et
                        res (…) bene laborare et gubernare seo meliorare debeamus nobis privatum
                        nomine usufructuandi (…). Censo: pro omni censum et iustitjam exinde tibi
                        vel ad subcessoribus tuis ad pars ipsius ecclesie Sancte Marie per singulos
                        annos, per omnem mense augusto, vobis reddere debeamus ad ipsa ecclesia
                        Sancti Marie vobis vel ad ministerialem vestro, quas ibi pre tempore
                        abueritis, argentum denarios bonos expendiviles numero triginta et sex; et a
                        mandato vestro venire debeamus hic Luca legem et iustitjam faciendum tantum
                        (…). Pena: spondeo cum meis heredes conponere tibi (…) penam argentum
                        soledos triginta (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>.Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Ostribertus"
                            >Ostripertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Teudaldus">Teudaldus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Stefanus">Stefanus</name></persName>,
                            <persName ref="#people/149" key="#Witness">Cunimundu</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/147">Lamberto</persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
